I have now checked your case about the rates mismatch from the app for both DHL Express and FedEx.
&nbsp;
   For DHL Express, the app is adding an EXPORT DECLARATION surcharge, which is applied for high value shipments. The default setup in the app uses a shipment value of 25000 (in local currency) for this surcharge to be added.  This value may not be accurate when shipping from Japan. Could you please reach out to the DHL team to confirm the correct threshold value above which this surcharge should apply for shipments from Japan?  Once confirmed, we will update the value in the app so that the rates are reflected correctly for your DHL Express shipments.
&nbsp;   For FedEx, the rates are not matching as Insurance Surcharge is being added by FedEx for International Shipments. We have contacted FedEx to get more information on this case and we will enhance the app to correctly show the rates from the app.  &nbsp;
Looking forward to your response about the DHL EXPORT DECLARATION shipment value.
&nbsp;
Thanks and Regards,
Touseef
